The Dialogues with Solzhenitsyn (Russian:   ) is a Russian television documentary by Russian filmmaker Alexander Sokurov on Aleksandr Solzhenitsyn. The documentary shot in Solzhenitsyns home shows his everyday life and covers his reflections on Russian history and literature.[1]
